Class RepInfoGroupRefImpl

java.lang.Object
info.oais.infomodel.implementation.InformationObjectRefImpl
info.oais.infomodel.implementation.RepresentationInformationRefImpl
info.oais.infomodel.implementation.representationinformation.RepInfoGroupRefImpl
All Implemented Interfaces:
InformationObject, RepresentationInformation, RepInfoGroup
Direct Known Subclasses:
RepInfoAndGroupRefImpl, RepInfoOrRefImpl
public class RepInfoGroupRefImpl extends RepresentationInformationRefImpl implements RepInfoGroup
RepresentationInformation as a Group, each of which may have a category e.g. Structure, Semantic or Other.
Each element is RepresentationInformation which may itself be a Group. Groups may be tagged as a RepInfoAndGroup or a RepInfoOrGroup by implementing the approriate interface. If neither is implemented then the default is that it is a RepInfoAndGroup.

David
